# FastAPI Development Standards

## Project Structure

```
src/
├── main.py                 # FastAPI app entry
├── config.py               # Settings
├── database.py             # DB connection
├── routers/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── users.py
│   └── posts.py
├── schemas/                # Pydantic models
│   ├── __init__.py
